1. Moj *profesor* matematike je veoma strog. (My *mathematics teacher* is very strict.)
2. *Profesora* engleskog jezika pitala sam za savet. (I asked the *English teacher* for advice.)
3. *Profesore*, da li biste mogli da mi objasnite ovo gradivo? (Excuse me, *professor*, could you explain this material to me?)
4. Moja sestra je upisala fakultet na kojem predaje njen omiljeni *profesor*. (My sister enrolled in a faculty where her favorite *professor* teaches.)
5. Za vikend sam srela svog bivšeg *profesora* biologije. (I ran into my former *biology teacher* over the weekend.)
6. *Profesorka* istorije je uvek veoma zahtevna u svojim ispitima. (The *history professor* is always very demanding in her exams.)
7. Novi *profesori* će početi da predaju od sledeće školske godine. (New *professors* will start teaching from the next school year.)
8. Škola organizuje skup za sve *profesore* kako bi se usaglasili oko nastavnog plana. (The school is organizing a meeting for all *teachers* to agree on the teaching plan.)